OL,3,CTeachers turning to antidepressants
OL,4,Cand alcohol to cope with work ` survey
OL,6,FTeachers are turning to
OL,7,Fantidepressants and alcohol to cope
OL,8,Fwith work pressures, a survey suggests.
OL,10,FMore than four in five (84%) teachers
OL,11,Fexperienced more work-related stress
OL,12,Fin the last year, according to a poll
OL,13,Fby the NASUWT teaching union.
OL,15,FThe survey, of 11,754 NASUWT members
OL,16,Fin the UK between October and December
OL,17,Flast year, suggests 86% of teachers
OL,18,Fbelieve that their job has adversely
OL,19,Faffected their mental health in the
OL,20,Flast 12 months.
