OL,6,FThe motion warns of a "rise in
OL,7,Fsuicide, suicide attempts and suicidal
OL,8,Fthoughts within the teaching
OL,9,Fprofession" and it says the union is
OL,10,Fconcerned the number will rise.
OL,12,FIt adds the pressures of the job are
OL,13,Fleading to "a mental health emergency"
OL,14,Fwithin the profession and teachers'
OL,15,Fhealth is reaching "a crisis point".
