OL,4,Cand alcohol to cope with work ` survey
OL,6,FNearly a quarter (23%) of teachers
OL,7,Fincreased their alcohol intake in the
OL,8,Fpast year because of work, while 12%
OL,9,Freported using or increasing their
OL,10,Freliance on antidepressants, according
OL,11,Fto the NASUWT poll.
OL,13,FAmong the members questioned, 3% said
OL,14,Fthey had self-harmed in the last 12
OL,15,Fmonths because of work.
OL,17,FIt comes after Ofsted has come under
OL,18,Fgreater scrutiny in the past year
OL,19,Fafter the suicide of headteacher Ruth
OL,20,FPerry.
