OL,6,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,7,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,8,FPrimary School in Reading, Berkshire,
OL,9,Ffrom its highest rating to its lowest
OL,10,Fover safeguarding concerns.
OL,12,FAnother motion, which was passed by
OL,13,FNASUWT delegates at the annual
OL,14,Fconference on Friday, called on the
OL,15,Funion executive to work with
OL,16,Finspectorates across the UK to provide
OL,17,Fguidance on how welfare and wellbeing
OL,18,Fcan be further prioritised and
OL,19,Finspection can be seen as a supportive
OL,20,Fprocess.
