OL,6,F"We need a two-pronged approach to
OL,7,Faddressing the epidemic of mental ill
OL,8,Fhealth among the teaching profession,
OL,9,Fwhich both tackles the factors driving
OL,10,Fwork-related stress, while also
OL,11,Fputting in place greater support
OL,12,Fsystems for teachers and school
OL,13,Fleaders."
OL,15,FDr Roach suggested that the picture on
OL,16,Fteacher wellbeing had "got worse".
