OL,6,FHe added: "It is clear we also need
OL,7,Fbetter welfare support in our schools
OL,8,Fand colleges to help teachers' manage
OL,9,Ftheir mental health and deal with what
OL,10,Fis an incredibly demanding job.
OL,12,F"The status quo is not an option. Too
OL,13,Fmany teachers are having their health
OL,14,Fdestroyed and others are leaving the
OL,15,Fprofession in a bid to save their
OL,16,Fsanity.
